{"title":"纪念孙中山先生九十周年诞辰感怀七绝四首","authors":["李济深"],"dates":[{"year":1956,"month":11,"day":1}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"纪念孙中山先生九十周年诞辰感怀七绝四首"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李济深"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（一）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国民革命缅前贤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋斗艰难四十年，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"中国自由平等愿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"至今应可慰重泉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（二）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史车轮进不停，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后生事业过先生，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虚心更是成功后，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"追念前贤愿共鸣。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（三）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反封反帝有先程，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌我应该认识清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"寄语先生私淑辈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勿因意气负生平。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（四）故步自封道不通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遗言天下在为公，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只求国泰民安乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"莫事斤斤论派宗。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}